/* KUMRAT SCOUTS OPEN GROUP UPPER DIR Single-file React component (default export) ready for deployment to Vercel / Netlify.

Notes for you:

Replace /logo.png in the public folder with your Kumrat Scouts logo (Markhor Scout logo etc).

The membership form uses Netlify Forms (no backend required). To use Netlify forms, deploy to Netlify and the form will collect submissions.

For Formspree or email, replace the form action accordingly.

This app is mobile-friendly, bilingual (English + Urdu), PWA-installable (basic manifest meta should be added separately), and uses Tailwind CSS classes.

To deploy on Vercel: create a new project and push this file as src/App.jsx in a React app created with create-react-app or Vite. Add Tailwind configuration.


Features included in this single file:

Header with logo and bilingual toggle

Home, About, Join Us (membership form), Documents, Gallery, Contact sections

Fillable membership form (Netlify-ready) with validation

Download links placeholders for bilingual PDFs

Simple gallery grid

Contact block with WhatsApp quick-link

Footer with signatures placeholders */


